title: The Twilight of World Steam (Train History).pdf
description:
The Twilight of World Steam
Madison Square Press | 1973 | ISBN: 0448024322 | English | 312 pages | PDF | 105.7 MB

Written by two steam enthusiasts, this book provides a last look at steam trains in 55 countries, from Argentina and Bangladesh to Vietnam and New Zealand. Provides action shots from around the world and informative captions about the equipment. Illustrated with over 550 black and white (and a few color) photos
